## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="74b27-169">Questa proprietà viene utilizzata solo in fase di progettazione, durante l'emissione a livello di codice di un'istanza del flusso di lavoro utilizzando il modello a oggetti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="74b27-169">This property is used only at design time, while programmatically emitting a workflow instance using the object model.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="74b27-170">Rappresenta l’XAML che fa riferimento al gestore eventi, non ancora compilato.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="74b27-170">It represents XAML that references the event handler, which has not been compiled yet.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="74b27-171">Questa proprietà contiene un elemento `Hashtable`, con coppie di valori nome evento/nome del gestore eventi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="74b27-171">This property contains a `Hashtable`, with event name and event handler name-value pairs.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="74b27-172">Dopo la compilazione, le proprietà dell'evento verrà associata direttamente al gestore.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="74b27-172">After compilation, the event property is associated directly with the handler.</span></span>  
  
 [!INCLUDE[DependencyPropertyRemark](~/includes/dependencypropertyremark-md.md)]  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="74b27-173">Nell'esempio seguente viene illustrato come impostare il valore della proprietà di dipendenza <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Serialization.WorkflowMarkupSerializer.EventsProperty>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="74b27-173">The following example shows how to set the value of the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Serialization.WorkflowMarkupSerializer.EventsProperty> dependency property.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
CodeActivity code1 = new CodeActivity();  
Hashtable eventsHashtable = new Hashtable();  
eventsHashtable.Add("ExecuteCode", "methodName1");  
code1.SetValue(WorkflowMarkupSerializer.EventsProperty, eventsHashtable);  
```
